predictions.article: Secretary Rollins Delivers Remarks at Commodity Classic, Announces Next Steps for Economic Disaster Relief
predictions.prediction: The announcement of the $30 billion economic and disaster relief package will lead to an increase in applications for the Emergency Commodity Assistance Program (E-CAP) by at least 20% within the next month.
